Package com.gemalto.mfs.mwsdk.provisioning.listener

Interface AuthenticationStateListener

public interface AuthenticationStateListener
Listener to handle callbacks while checking Authentication is needed or not.
See Also:
AuthenticationState

  • Method Summary

    Modifier and Type Method Description
    void onError​(SDKError<NeedsAuthenticationErrorCode> error)
    This is the callback method called when need for authentication could not be verified due to an error.
    void onSuccess​(AuthenticationState authenticationState)
    This is callback method called when need for authentication is verified.

  • Method Details

    • onSuccess

      void onSuccess​(AuthenticationState authenticationState)
      This is callback method called when need for authentication is verified. See @ReplenishmentPrepService
      Parameters:
      authenticationState - the state of authentication.

    • onError

      void onError​(SDKError<NeedsAuthenticationErrorCode> error)
      This is the callback method called when need for authentication could not be verified due to an error.
      Parameters:
      error - the error code occurred during authentication.
